sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant C as ClientA / ClientB
  participant SSO as SSO Server
  participant R as Redis

  U->>C: Click Logout All Devices
  C->>SSO: POST /logout-all (Bearer access_token)

  SSO->>SSO: verifySession(access_token)
  SSO->>R: SMEMBERS userSessions:{userId}

  loop for each sessionId in userSessions
    SSO->>R: GET session:{sessionId}
    SSO->>R: DEL session:{sessionId}
    SSO->>R: SREM userSessions:{userId} sessionId
    alt session has device binding
      SSO->>R: DEL deviceSession:{deviceType}:{deviceId}
    end
  end

  SSO->>R: DEL userSessions:{userId}
  SSO-->>C: 200 {message: "global logout success"}

  Note over C,SSO: Any device using old access_token now fails verifySession
  C->>SSO: GET /session-info (token from another device)
  SSO-->>C: 401 Unauthorized